{"id":275598,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/global-voices-伊朗：呈现空气污染问题/","date":"2013-01-21T19:00:15Z","modified":"2013-01-21T19:00:15Z","title":"Global Voices | 伊朗：呈现空气污染问题","content":"<p><p><img title=\"Tehran and Pollution\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/irna2-375x243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"243\" /></p>\n<p>多年来，空气污染为伊朗无数民众公敌，政府有时因为严重空污，宣布公务机关停班一日，如今已稀松平常。</p>\n<p>元月初，卫生部<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.mehrnews.com/fa/newsdetail.aspx?NewsID=1783975\">公布数据</a>，去年因空污影响，首都德黑兰超过4400人丧命。</p>\n<p><strong>灰蒙蒙的德黑兰</strong></p>\n<p>国内网络民众之间流传着数则漫画，皆与首都污染情况有关。Omid在<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://iroon.com/irtn/cartoon/161/\">Iroon.com</a>网站上发表一幅漫画，描绘首都一片灰扑扑。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://iroon.com/irtn/cartoon/161/\"><img title=\"Pollution in Tehran\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/omid2-318x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"318\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>图片来源：Omid，Iroon.com</p>\n</div>\n<p>Mana Neyastani在有关污染的<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mardomak.org/cartoons/full/75527\">漫画</a>里，亦不忘政治：祖父说，“又到早晨，我该起床…这一切的坏消息…处决、监狱…”，他深吸一口气，准备开始一天，却立刻倒下，身旁的报纸头条写着，“首都空气污染致命”。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mardomak.org/cartoons/full/75527\"><img title=\"Pollution\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/manapollution-264x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>图片来源：Mana Neyestani，Mardomak</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>黑暗城市</strong></p>\n<p>以下影片里，藉由飞机降落在Mahrabad机场，呈现出首都午间污染多么严重。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n<p><strong>无氧</strong></p>\n<p>伊朗博客Zeyton<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://zeytooooooon.wordpress.com/2013/01/05/%D8%A2%D9%82%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%AD%DA%A9%D9%88%D9%85%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%B7%D9%84%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%86-%D9%BE%D8%B4%D9%8A%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%86-%DA%AF/\">表示</a>波斯语：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们以前常说，这个国家无处可呼吸，是指政府的社会与政治迫害，但如今国内却名符其实，真的无氧气可呼吸。这个政府连氧气都无法提供给人民，却宣称要将治理制度外销到全世界。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>除了首都之外，全国诸多城市亦为污染受害者，例如南部城市<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://fararu.com/fa/news/138098/%D8%AA%D8%B5%D8%A7%D9%88%DB%8C%D8%B1-%D9%88%D8%B6%D8%B9%DB%8C%D8%AA-%D9%88%D8%AE%DB%8C%D9%85-%D8%A2%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AF%DA%AF%DB%8C-%D9%87%D9%88%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D9%87%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B2\">Ahwaz</a>波斯语。</p>\n<div>校对：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/farid/\" title=\"文章导读 Farid\">Farid</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/01/17/tehrans-deadly-air-pollution-illustrated/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/01/21/12103/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F01%2F21%2F12103%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F01%2F21%2F12103%2F&#038;desc=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%88%E7%8E%B0%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F01%2F21%2F12103%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalv